#!/bin/bash
# Script to generate a premium retro high-tech hacker terminal loading video for Plexishow.
# Fades in lines of tech logs mimicking a real-time decryption and GPU loading sequence.
# Pure black background and matrix green text to optimize compression size.
# Perfectly matches IPTV stream parameters: 1920x1080 Full HD, AAC Stereo 48kHz.

